      /*... */
      exit_shell();
      return 0;
    }
   ```
   This fix defines the `exit()` function as a macro in the `utils.h` header
   file, which will call the `exit()` function correctly. This fix addresses the
   root cause of the issue and will prevent the crash in the future.
   
